      <title>阿根廷推动新计划期间米莱将与国际货币基金组织总裁会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-to-meet-imf-chief-amid-argentina-s-push-for-new-program</link>
